# Stack Buddy environment variables.
#
# Copy this file to .env. The deterministic calculator works without any
# environment configuration — these are only here so you can override the
# default port if 2034 is taken.
#
# DO NOT commit .env. The .gitignore in this repo already excludes it.
#
# Stack Buddy does not call any LLM. To reason through your plan with an AI,
# paste private-ai/prompt.md into Maple, Venice, or any other LLM chat. See
# private-ai/README.md for the workflow.

# Backend port. Defaults to 2034 if unset.
# PORT=
